        <briefdescription>
<para>Submits a command for deferred processing. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Called by the <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1messaging_1_1command_1_1TypedCommandBuffer" kindref="compound">TypedCommandBuffer</ref> during flush when a handler is registered for this command type. The handler typically enqueues the command for batch processing during Manager::flush().</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>cmd</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The command to process.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>True if the command was accepted. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
